Vandetanib plus gemcitabine versus placebo plus gemcitabine in locally advanced 
or metastatic pancreatic carcinoma (ViP): a prospective, randomised, 
double-blind, multicentre phase 2 trial.

Middleton G(1), Palmer DH(2), Greenhalf W(3), Ghaneh P(3), Jackson R(3), Cox 
T(3), Evans A(3), Shaw VE(3), Wadsley J(4), Valle JW(5), Propper D(6), Wasan 
