Health-adjusted life expectancy in HIV-positive and HIV-negative men and women 
in British Columbia, Canada: a population-based observational cohort study.

Hogg RS(1), Eyawo O(2), Collins AB(2), Zhang W(3), Jabbari S(3), Hull MW(4), 
Lima VD(4), Ahmed T(3), Kendall CE(5), Althoff KN(6), Justice AC(7), Barrios 
